    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained and still has plenty of life left for all your adventures! It's super reliable, comfortable, and ready for a new home. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
