    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving, naturally aspirated 4.0L S65 V8. The powerplant retains its signature linear power delivery and sharp throttle response, facilitated by individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,250 RPM redline. This unit is mated to a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox, ensuring maximum engagement. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The chassis remains balanced with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates, while the M-Variable differential ensures optimal torque vectoring across the rear axle. The subframe and bushings remain tight, offering precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the aesthetics show honest character from spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity are excellent.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Reliable engine. Clean title. Interior is well-maintained. Minor exterior wear.",
