    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of reliability and care, offering a balanced blend of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though a discerning eye might find a few minor stone chips consistent with light road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats remain supple and supportive, and all onboard technology\u2014from the premium sound system to the navigation\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and oil service. It shifts smoothly, brakes confidently, and sits on a set of high-tread tires ready for the seasons ahead. With a clear title and a smoke-free interior, this is a well-maintained daily driver that provides a premium experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
