      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and careful stewardship. This well-maintained specimen offers a seamless integration of performance and comfort, ensuring a superior driving experience. Both the exterior finish and interior appointments have been preserved to a high standard, reflecting a commitment to automotive excellence. This offering represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning professional seeking a dependable asset of proven caliber.",
