      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super well-maintained and still has plenty of life left in it. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is reliable, comfy, and honestly a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and ready to hit the road today. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have!",
