    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, facilitated by six individual throttle bodies and a recalibrated Double VANOS system. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with upgraded bushings and a reinforced subframe, ensuring structural rigidity during high-lateral G maneuvers. Recently serviced with a focus on valve clearances and a cooling system overhaul, this M3 offers a pure mechanical connection for the discerning pilot.",
